  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::Bonbibi.DialogueLine
  speaker: 0
  text: You don't remember running to the bank. You remember the roar, and then you
    remember the bank. Dhona's boat was already in the water. His men were already
    rowing. He didn't look back.
